{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20231.jpg","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"Act 2","narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":50.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":37.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"Chapter 5@\"Those Left Behind\"","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":37.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event08","chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"That appearance is from long before she became a@Witch and underwent a great transformation...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"In fact, even long before Minou and her other@daughters were born."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"That was Isabeau in her youth, back when she was@a Magical Girl."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":810000}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Perenelle & Nicolas","textCenter":"...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901},{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Melissa & Elisa","textCenter":"...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textBg":"shout","textRight":"...What did you say?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Probably about forty years ago, around the time@of the appearance of the red moon,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"she launched an attack to hinder our movements."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"There are only two more books left in the Ark...@The situation is leaning in our favor."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Qube, do you know something?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Yeah, I have a clear idea of what's going on."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Forty years ago, around the year 1400,@the world diverged into two branches."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"One where Tart was born,@and one where she wasn't."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The cause of the world splitting was Isabeau@peering into the future."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_31031.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":412200,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"id":412200}],"nameCenter":"Isabeau","textCenter":"I have glimpsed a far distant future.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":412200}],"nameCenter":"Isabeau","textCenter":"In the events to come, the only one who can thwart@my plan..."},{"chara":[{"id":412200}],"nameCenter":"Isabeau","textCenter":"Is the one called La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"id":412200}],"nameCenter":"Isabeau","textCenter":"Or so I thought..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"The far distant future...is that the future I came@from?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Indeed..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"I can't for certain how far into the future@it lies, however..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"\"France will be destroyed by a woman,\""},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"\"but shall be saved by a girl.\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"According to this prophecy,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Isabeau's ambitions were shattered by La Pucelle,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"and the legend of Jeanne La Pucelle"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"has been passed down to Kagome's era."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"By knowing this, she can act in a way that prevents@the birth of La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"As a result, the branched world without La Pucelle"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"is the world of the red moon, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Most likely."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Nicolas","textLeft":"The world is swaying between these two@possibilities."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameLeft":"Nicolas","textLeft":"If the erosion of the red moon's world intensifies,@the memories of La Pucelle will disappear,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameLeft":"Nicolas","textLeft":"but if we can keep her existence anchored,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameLeft":"Nicolas","textLeft":"the original world will return..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Overall, what Nicolas says is correct."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Even if he can't hear me,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"he seems to be insightfully aware."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Tart doesn't exist and nobody can stop Isabeau's@ambitions."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"That's the world of the red moon."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Indeed, in Kagome's era, humanity's presence had@vanished."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_19131.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It's an all too reasonable conclusion","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"for where Isabeau's ambitions lead."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Don't say something so terrifying so lightly!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
